---
title: Plum & Oyster Beef Stir-Fry with Veggies, Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: A plum and oyster sauce is a richly decadent addition to any dish, but when it accompanies stir-fried beef and veggies in garlic rice it transforms into a taste sensation that you won’t be forgetting any time soon.

